snippet.title: *NSFW* CarsFuckingDragons Trailer
snippet.description:
The trailer for "CarsFuckingDragons" from NecroCatic Games. Available to wishlist on STEAM here : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1678700/CarsFuckingDragons/

RELEASING OCT 1, 2021.

Thank you GRIZLEY for making the trailer - @BakayaroEd (on Twitter). 

The game comes* out October 1st, 2021!!

-Make sure to check out www.reddit.com/r/carsfuckingdragons for more action- And why yes, the music for the game was done by the creator of the subreddit, GuitarPlayer0171 (Dr.Quincy)!!

www.necrocaticgames.com  "Love It To Death!"
